Choose 2. You may choose the same mode more than once;
* The next card you play this turn with an effect that deals arcane damage, instead deals that much arcane damage plus 1.
* Draw a card.

**Once per Turn Instant** -- Put a face down card from your arsenal on the bottom of your deck: Gain {r}
**Arcane Barrier 1** _(If your hero would be dealt arcane damage, you may pay {r} to prevent 1 of that damage.)_
**Blade Break** _(When the combat chain closes, if this defended, destroy it.)_

**Twice per Turn Instant** -- {r}: You may put an arrow card from your hand face up into an empty arsenal zone you control. If you do, choose 1;
* It gains +1{p} until end of turn.
* It gains **go again** until end of turn.
